for instance, we have been successful in penetrating the affinity card segment in australia, where we issue cards with the majority of the largest professional associations in that country. in australia, affinity cards are a substantial part of our
total revolving portfolio and contribute to our proprietary consumer lending activities.  as in the united states, rewards programs are a
